FBIS3-23294 "jptot011__l94110" JPRS-TOT-94-011-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 7 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA LEBANON `Terrorists' Kill SLA Soldier's Wife TA0703113694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1100 GMT 7 Mar 94 TA0703113694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] Exchanges of gunfire are currently taking place in south Lebanon between terrorists, the IDF [Israel Defense Forces], and the SLA [South Lebanese Army] after the terrorists killed three SLA soldiers this morning, kidnapped two, and killed the wife of another soldier in several separate raids. Our correspondent Yo'av Aviv reports that Hizballah has announced that it is holding the two captured SLA soldiers.
